main event: A light was observed for about 30 minutes in Burlington, Massachusetts in 1965.
interesting points: The light moved in a manner inconsistent with any known light source, including in front of a cloud.
The witness was very interested in UFOs and had corresponded with Project Blue Book before.
The report mentions previous sightings of 13 or more lights on multiple occasions.
The report is considered unreliable by Project Blue Book.
The witness requested more information on UFOs sightings across the United States.
